{"tid":1565171,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］今晚青山要人！！！","createTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T18:32:37.000Z","uid":159507,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b482a51422aced8957c36a6cf8648e7f3b295b46","tid":1565171,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>獅子山今晚會有爬山人鏈活動 而大西北既牛亦都唔可以執輸<br />\n今晚八月十五月圓之夜梗係要登上青山啦！<br />\n希望各位大西北既牛隻可以今晚一齊上黎照亮屯門 光復青山！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2pMdheT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2pMdheT.jpg&h=ee9b66b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n913 青雲站 8:00 pm 入青山<br />\n中秋佳節。港島太平山，九龍獅子山皆有慶典。一群新界屯門牛捨易取難，夜登青山（香港三尖之一），鍛鍊身心，挑戰自我。<br />\n期待各方加盟或share! <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=f4be742c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA</a><br />\n<br />\n行程及裝備：<br />\n2000: 輕鐡青雲站. 恭候大家🙇🏻&zwj;♂️ 。裝備 final check. <br />\n<br />\n依實際情況，分批起步。第一批A，第二批B.....如此類推<br />\n<br />\n為安全起見，每批至少一位老手 （上青山 6次），帶路，有適量急救用品。<br />\n出發，及到達checkpoint 時，必須停下，等齊人, 在TG 報平安。<br />\n例：&rdquo;B team, checkpoint 2，5 人，各人狀態良好！&rdquo;<br />\n然後才前進。<br />\n安全落山後，最後一次報平安，才解散。令其他屯門牛都放心，真正齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\nCheckpoint<br />\n 1. 青山寺. 入山前祈願：為此行求平安，為屯門求福氣，為香港求民主。<br />\n 2. 綠屋仔。再勇都要回下氣。等埋隊友，點齊人數，齊上齊落！<br />\n 3. 韓凌片石，百年古亭。承先啟後，頂峰在望，最後休整！<br />\n<br />\n2030: 最後一批起步,包括Admin。公佈上青山總人數，通知 屯門公園大group Admin.<br />\n<br />\n2200:  到達山頂。亮燈，照耀屯門。（記得通知地面的牛牛，幫我地影相！😄）<br />\n2230: 回程下山<br />\n2330:到青雲站解散。各自各精彩✌🏼<br />\n<br />\n裝備：<br />\n- 身體狀況良好，有行山經驗。要直上500 幾米，夜行更有難度。夜間口訣：黑泥白石光水氹。<br />\n<br />\n- 最少1 公升水。沿途冇補給，溪都冇<br />\n-小量食物<br />\n<br />\n- 長袖風衣，帽。山頂 24 小時好大風及凍。<br />\n-行山仗。<br />\n-蚊怕水<br />\n<br />\n- 急救用品（如有，山上只能自己救自己）<br />\n<br />\n玩樂<br />\n- 強力電筒，鐳射槍 唔少得！<br />\n- 其他無任歡迎。如果你有本事帶上去，再帶返落。<br />\n<br />\n有意見歡迎發表，補充🤗<br />\n群組<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FKgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QR6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=f4be742c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/Kgu4rxSW_h-ALEvqU94gBA</a>"},{"pid":"4a909d141f8fe20f227470f6a2750af304cea51e","tid":1565171,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:34.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"2cb76f531e41b52e018a0bdc63aa7f2407933153","tid":1565171,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"24f9291077fa2616829aafef93addb90670cc0c8","tid":1565171,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"592205b518001ae09fb3e0cbbd7cf62d065db25b","tid":1565171,"uid":30201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:57:59.000Z","msg":"中秋自選活動 祝大家平平安安 團團圓圓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n►人鏈活動◄<br />\n1630 石硤尾聯校人鏈&gt;集合點: 黃棣珊中學正門<br />\n1930 屯門牛牛人鏈&gt;集合點: 顯發里對出空地<br />\n2100 將軍澳人鏈&gt;調景嶺站&rarr;單車公園&larr;寶康公園<br />\n2130 沙田城門河人鏈 (直接去最接近你既河邊集合)<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►快閃大合唱◄<br />\n1300 中環&gt;遮打花園<br />\n1300 太古&gt;OIE樓下水池<br />\n1930 屯門&gt;顯發里對出空地<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►獅子山之路，齊慶中秋夜◄<br />\n1900 大圍、樂富、黃大仙等入口集合<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n►18區賞燈晚會 ◄ (如無注明則2030開始)<br />\n【新界西】<br />\n屯門顯發里對出空地 (承接大合唱)<br />\n屯門公園<br />\n天水圍公園<br />\n元朗公園<br />\n荃灣公園海濱長廊<br />\n葵涌運動場籃球場，林士德遊樂場<br />\n青衣海濱長廊<br />\n【新界東】<br />\n1900 上水陳融中學旁紅場<br />\n沙田中央公園<br />\n大埔海濱公園 ，大埔中央公園<br />\n馬鞍山公園<br />\n將軍澳海濱公園，寶康公園<br />\n【九龍】<br />\n美孚嶺南之風<br />\n長沙灣遊樂場<br />\n深水埗通州街遊樂場<br />\n尖沙咀梳士巴利道公園<br />\n黃大仙廣場 ，摩士公園<br />\n觀塘海濱公園<br />\n油塘道遊樂場<br />\n2100 紅磡碼頭<br />\n2150 慈雲山中央球場大合唱<br />\n【港島】<br />\n維園中央草坪<br />\n鰂魚涌至西灣河海濱長廊<br />\n柴灣公園<br />\n【東涌】<br />\n東涌海濱長廊，百慕達公園<br />\n【離島】<br />\n2115 長洲東灣"},{"pid":"9a2615b52f4b162a9a99f0e62cc5cd023687914d","tid":1565171,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:58:14.000Z","msg":"光復青山，照耀青山<br />\n手足一定上呀喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e8fd4f0231bc35c3cf68ff3f6aa23c175c8ae6","tid":1565171,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:58:29.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"fbb36f37ac63de16ff770bc1822cdc6cc677b18b","tid":1565171,"uid":159507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T04:58:40.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"